{"tid":1101460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎智英：「會員制挽救了紐約時報的衰落，也等於說報紙有得救了」","createTime":"2019-04-11T04:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T11:33:25.000Z","uid":64694,"like":21,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"cd68884abc617d6ee662ee3f0cbf9376da308d23","tid":1101460,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:54:05.000Z","msg":"《蘋果日報》試圖改變收費模式的想法，其實早已有跡可尋。壹傳媒創辦人<span style=\"color: red;\">黎智英</span>上月在其專欄撰文，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為會員收費制能令報紙重生</span>：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我是報紙經營者，十多年前開始悲嘆，報紙快要被時代淘汰從歷史舞台中離場了。我錯了，想不到報紙在網上以電子形式出現加上會員制，重生了，不單止重生，這新的生命比過去更光明遠大。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n他以美國《紐約時報》為例，指其電子版訂戶達260萬，每年收入6億美元，連廣告收入比以前純粹賣報紙更好賺，「<span style=\"color: red;\">會員制挽救了紐約時報的衰落，也等於說報紙有得救了</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thestand.news/society/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%88-%E6%88%96%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestand.news%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E6%2597%25A9-%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2589%2588-%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E8%25A8%2582%25E9%2596%25B1%2F&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=1bd9a94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestand.news/society/%E5%8D%97%E6%97%A9-%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%89%88-%E6%88%96%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%94%B9%E7%82%BA%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E8%A8%82%E9%96%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"370774fda17de16ba7e3b7579503369d57e8eb8c","tid":1101460,"uid":470,"like":174,"dislike":4,"score":170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠膽自比nyt<br />\n幾時唔用支那用語 同放棄報tvb啲垃圾劇新聞呀"},{"pid":"a82796510c058f369a1f2076f9c0374c9830b596","tid":1101460,"uid":64694,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"原來學紐約時報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f2fc668003d71761be6a521cd0404092d5d454","tid":1101460,"uid":170309,"like":60,"dislike":3,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"人地幾high quality<br />\ncnbc 俾成一百蚊港紙一個月都會訂<br />\nBBC （唔睇commentary)"},{"pid":"5ac18d585dfe3ec03d339ae68c78441f4b8e2ad9","tid":1101460,"uid":54733,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"人地深度專題報導 你就風化新聞 邊有得比"},{"pid":"c976477100e969b1fff4fa6ad1a373716821d953","tid":1101460,"uid":82532,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"5ac18d585dfe3ec03d339ae68c78441f4b8e2ad9","tid":1101460,"uid":54733,"like":127,"dislike":1,"score":126,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:06:02.000Z","msg":"人地深度專題報導 你就風化新聞 邊有得比"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"有事嗰陣都會睇佢唧牙膏嘅"},{"pid":"d91cc253a5bc40d81e98d12cee5a69d6dae8b162","tid":1101460,"uid":217275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4500e90657466404f1f25a1900158a1a43a427e6","tid":1101460,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"樂觀是他最大本公"},{"pid":"1035fd7536fc7dd828655d49b08d5eeb646841a3","tid":1101460,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"樂觀是他最大本錢"},{"pid":"73f069581f42ddf6c2a502ccbd5240ee3f44e18e","tid":1101460,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"香港人 請繼續含撚支持蘋果日報 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aaef0fa7c5173079473c40413dca76fb4464554","tid":1101460,"uid":35014,"like":69,"dislike":2,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"959d2c90dcc4ca1493e0e49265b3cf0de2ba8d36","tid":1101460,"uid":32473,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:19:55.000Z","msg":"兩睇啦<br />\n佢平時d報導真係唔高質<br />\n係睇佢地有事果陣既唧牙膏"},{"pid":"6a7653deebd734b8032df4ca6c3437a3d6e90ebc","tid":1101460,"uid":202698,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:20:50.000Z","msg":"唔了解人地美國閱讀文化就抄人地，隨時死得仲快<br />\nNYTimes本身特點就唔係以鬥快出新聞，係以新聞內容深度為特色<br />\n<br />\n以前人地美國佬習慣每日起身果陣，邊食住早餐邊拎住份NYTimes睇新聞專題／評論<br />\n依家科技轉變，就邊食住早餐，邊拎住個IPad睇專題／評論<br />\n<br />\n香港以乜野為特色？？快速+廣泛，從來都唔係深度<br />\n（本身蘋果既新聞就已經無深度可言）<br />\n以香港黎講，一間傳媒機構，最重要既就係公眾傳播能力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次蘋果set左會員制，就已經與公眾落左一道閘先， 閹左自己既公眾傳播能力，相關資訊只可以係自己既支持者/會員/讀者先有得睇<br />\n<br />\n即係公眾無得再公開取閱有相資訊（公眾隨便係街到打網址係睇唔到蘋果新聞）<br />\n講得再難聽d，蘋果日報即係廢左自己係香港既公眾傳播能力，即係自閹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥佬黎今次真係蝕到上晒腦，想抄人地NYTimes模式但又忽視香港讀者既閱讀習慣，畫虎不成反類犬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個可能性：　<br />\n一，短期內點擊數大跌，急急腳取消會員制度<br />\n二，堅持行會員制度，等執笠"},{"pid":"cde2dfe52a35ad48e5c4b211c3e5e4e940a3bd0b","tid":1101460,"uid":60164,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:21:02.000Z","msg":"要市民比錢供養中共白手套<br />\n不了<br />\n<br />\n要供都唔供你建制b隊總舵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53829813534ff679f40456ffe39253ffc81e46d2","tid":1101460,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:22:28.000Z","msg":"東施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cd3ea5d82383ef4f5435b6d25e81afc3b9a73f","tid":1101460,"uid":202698,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"之前肥佬黎想借動腦Q黎搏讀者登記做會員<br />\n第一步係動腦Q，第二度就係依家SET免費會員制，第三步就係收費<br />\n<br />\n每一步都係邁向緊死亡"},{"pid":"efcf1da9841d7b4700edd89f80136f64fbfc5f33","tid":1101460,"uid":2126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:23:30.000Z","msg":"同times比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aefc1f5d877e4e3505e8